um6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DFN%26message%3D6627045%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7ad619bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6627045&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6647558&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6647558%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D0&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b4066144\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6647558&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6660937&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6660937%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D0&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=aa5fde17\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6660937&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6674860&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6674860%26page%3D1&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cdff2cce\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6674860&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6691068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DFN%26message%3D6691068&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c191fb72\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=FN&amp;message=6691068</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6707896&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6707896%26page%3D1&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d1330862\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6707896&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6728926&amp;type=BW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6728926%26type%3DBW&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=30452853\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6728926&amp;type=BW</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUwants個邊既分析帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D18785349%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26page%3D1&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRF0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2d893d6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=18785349&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;page=1</a></div>"},{"pid":"038010c96fe0420bcff951eef45e300433d1de66","tid":279402,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">若果CD-ROM想加入群組的話<br />\n<br />\n可以自行去Uwants 開個新帳號<br />\n<br />\n之後再按照格式PM老夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(CD-ROM即是沒有高登帳號的人士) </div>"},{"pid":"d4cc2f2d20d0f7b0cad926ed39f760f83005c1fe","tid":279402,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T09:11:33.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價現時正在打造雙頂回落<br />\n<br />\n(4月17日的高位1295.1及6月6日的高位1296.1形成雙頂)<br />\n<br />\n5月9日至6月6日此段期間 金價有可能正運行第五浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n若果運用黃金比率去計算的話<br />\n<br />\n0.5倍黃金比率剛好是1300心理關口<br />\n<br />\n故金價在1296.1時掉頭回落也是合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計法如下:<br />\n<br />\n第一至第三浪波幅: 1295.1-1122.6 = 172.5<br />\n<br />\n1213.7+172.5*0.5 = 1300 (心理關口)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以金價有可能借雙頂回落引起ABC下跌浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留意星期五出現大陰燭跌穿10天及20天WMA<br />\n<br />\n亦跌穿Keltner Channel 中軸及日本雲層圖轉勢線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期一可能會繼續下跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但跌至基準線及Keltner Channel底線附近可能會暫停跌勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n現階段來說<br />\n<br />\n星期一可以試試沽貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期二至星期四則要隨機應變,相機行事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n金價現正打造雙頂回落<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/2a7Cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F2a7Cbc.jpg&h=124779e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42b99fea3c53a1dad7cd0264fb8be89c2bc04a97","tid":279402,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:43:33.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價於6月9日出現大陰燭跌穿10天WMA,轉勢線及Keltner Channel中軸後<br />\n<br />\n其後2天出現膠著的狀態<br />\n<br />\n6月13日出現小型上升鎚,並沿50天及基準線反彈<br />\n<br />\n金價在6月14日夜晚時份開始急劇攀升,先升穿10天,20天WMA<br />\n<br />\n其後更升穿Keltner Channel中軸及轉勢線,本來有望收復失地<br />\n<br />\n但在凌晨2點,美聯儲公佈利率決議後,金價出現急跌<br />\n<br />\n大陽燭演變為射擊之星<br />\n<br />\n6月15日再出現大陰燭跌穿基準線,50天WMA及100天WMA<br />\n<br />\n金價昨天雖然出現十字星,在100天WMA及Keltner Channel底線徘徊<br />\n<br />\n但本日早上再次受壓於100天WMA,T並跌入雲層內部及跌穿Keltner Channel底線<br />\n<br />\n現時弱勢已成,金價有可能會藉此運行ABC下跌浪<br />\n<br />\n即市最大支持位為250天WMA的1240.9<br />\n<br />\n萬一金價再出現特大陰燭跌穿250天WMA的話,基本上可以確定回力無天<br />\n<br />\n後市極有可能會不停急跌<br />\n<br />\n今天可以輕倉沽貨/等到價位到達1240.9再搏反彈<br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下圖可以看到金價受壓於100天WMA,並跌穿Keltner Channel 底線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/224231_e98e895e82a25f92ff0632783d277010.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F224231_e98e895e82a25f92ff0632783d277010.JPG&h=801f600e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a982fcabb73461ba6145ae3a04830bcbf2e7b23","tid":279402,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n老夫也有一個月沒出分析了<br />\n<br />\n今天難得有少少時間     所以打篇分析出來給諸君參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上文提及到金價弱勢已成,會藉雙頂回落運行ABC下跌浪<br />\n<br />\n其後金價於7月3日出現特大陰燭跌穿250天WMA及Keltner Channel底線<br />\n<br />\n7月7日再出現陰燭跌穿Bollinger Bands底線<br />\n<br />\n但7月10日開始出現上升鎚    其後冉冉上升<br />\n<br />\n現時更突破日本雲層圖轉勢線<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n若果運用波浪理論去分析的話,現時可以歸納出以下幾種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.金價現時正在運行A浪 (下跌浪的開始)<br />\n<br />\n2.金價現時正在運行C浪 (破壞性下跌浪)<br />\n<br />\n3.金價現時正在運行B浪  (反彈浪)<br />\n<br />\n4.ABC下跌浪已行完,7月10日出現那支上升鎚是指示金價開展新循環的第一浪<br />\n(上升浪)<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n鑑於分析的過程比較繁複     所以論據在此省略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以老夫先說分析的結果<br />\n<br />\n現時無法百分之一百確認金價是處於第幾浪<br />\n<br />\n但發生機率按照遞減掛序的話,可以歸納出<br />\n<br />\n情況(3)  &gt;   情況(1)  &gt;  情況 (2)  &gt; 情況 (4)<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n即是現時金價運行B浪反彈浪的機會比較大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已知B浪起點是7月10日的低位1204.7<br />\n<br />\n若果運用黃金比率去計算的話<br />\n<br />\n可以得知金價升至250天WMA及100天WMA附近時可能會完成B浪<br />\n<br />\n並且會出現急跌的現象<br />\n<br />\n相關計算如下:<br />\n<br />\n1204.7+91.4*0.236    =1226.2<br />\n<br />\n1204.7+91.4*0.382    =1239.6  (250天WMA附近)<br />\n<br />\n1204.7+91.4*0.5      =1250.4    (100天WMA附近)<br />\n<br />\n1204.7+91.4*0.618    =1261.2<br />\n<br />\n1204.7+91.4*0.786    =1276.5<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n但現階段來說    仍未可以判斷到金價行第幾浪<br />\n<br />\n亦未可以判斷到金價運行哪個黃金比率<br />\n<br />\n現時先當金價正在運行情況 (3)<br />\n<br />\n下星期的入市策略為等待價位升至250天WMA時再考慮沽貨<br />\n<br />\n其後再隨機應變,相機行事<br />\n<br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/120658_56bff505b52c74c648e020ff42dd4bb3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F120658_56bff505b52c74c648e020ff42dd4bb3.JPG&h=652eeb1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d8c0a364d2dd5ef457beec406aa7fb76589089","tid":279402,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"本日分析:<br />\n<br />\n金價升至0.5倍黃金比率1250.6時沒有出現顯著的回落<br />\n<br />\n看來此個波浪未必是B浪 / 下跌浪<br />\n<br />\n有可能循環已經終結,現時有可能正在運行第一浪<br />\n<br />\n而金價已升穿日本雲層圖基準線及轉勢線,並升穿250天WMA及100天WMA<br />\n<br />\nWMA亦出現短期入貨訊號<br />\n<br />\n價位今天有可能繼續冉冉上升,但升至雲層頂部時有可能受阻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃金每日一單:<br />\n<br />\n現時為2017年7月25日下午2:04分       買入價位為1257.5         建議買入黃金<br />\n<br />\n止賺:1266.5                     止蝕:1252<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對沖策略:<br />\n<br />\n買入:1257.5             止賺:1266.5             止蝕:1252.5<br />\n<br />\n賣出:1257                止賺:1244.1             止蝕:1262<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/140839_889cf7979626266b90b39d824b3a6116.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F140839_889cf7979626266b90b39d824b3a6116.JPG&h=1a851049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cb628395563a4feaedee392a2ffff852f050e8a","tid":279402,"uid":154512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"請問依家仲有冇得申請入群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829aae0d4fa45338e8107661f1c6b78efbb5d88b","tid":279402,"uid":44798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}